                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a niece to a pawnbroker; I never saw the prisoner; I took this watch from one 
               <persName id="t17860719-95-person993">
                  Simon
                   Connel
               <interp inst="t17860719-95-person993" type="surname" value="Connel"></interp>
